oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The Unexplained Abortion
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Kennedy, Peter C.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The title of this presentation was assigned me by the program committee. It probably represents wishful thinking on their part as much as any real expectation. On the other hand, they may have been trying to give me as wide a range for discussion as possible and since currently the great majority of bovine abortion are unexplained we have considerable scope.
